<p>title:</p>
<p>Similar to the <a href="https://creativebibliolatry.wordpress.com/2019/05/31/book-of-the-month-diaspora-by-greg-egan/">book Diaspora by Greg Egan</a>, this Hugo Award sci-fi story written by Cixin Liu associates elaborate scientific ideas like the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Three-body_problem">Three-Body Problem</a> with a creative and entrancing plot.</p>
